{
  "stem": "27409.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So they took me in the kitchens, were only too glad, for there was two soldiers working.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So they were only glad to give me the job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I understood everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There were German and Walon there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were volunteers from Belgium was there, and a Slovak unit, which were in-- in Berdichev.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Afterwards, I heard they had also labor soldier, Hungarian, but I didn't see them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked with them a few days, and then I had my-- all the time was in-- in connection-- I had my connection to my unit.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they were ready to go, our transport, they had very small garrisons in villages.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We sent them ammunition and food out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I know it's myself and-- and my group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They giving a reception.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to run back to my group because they would have known that I am the one who was a traitor, if I could call it so.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we were-- we went all the time in Vinnytsia Oblast.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From there, we went into Galicia, always attacking German garrison, putting-- mining the railways to killing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went up to the Carpathian as we knew we were supposed to go over the Carpathian in Slovakia where they prepared in Banska Bystrica a resistance out of all the Slovaks.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we never reached it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- the local population, [NON-ENGLISH], gave us over to the German, OR sold for sugar.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nearly all our group was killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We returned 27 on three sledges back to Ukraine-- Vinnytsia, from where our unit came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There we started again getting orders from Korpak, our commanding officer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was in the time of Stalingrad, Korsun-Shevchenkivskyi where the big battles were.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
